Welcome to Scala 2.13.9 (Java HotSpot(TM) 64-Bit Server VM, Java 19).
Type in expressions for evaluation. Or try :help.

scala> val name = "Andrey Shevchenko"
val name: String = Andrey Shevchenko

scala> println(s"Hello Scala! This is $name")
Hello Scala! This is Andrey Shevchenko

scala> val greet = List("Hello", "Hola","Guten tag")
val greet: List[String] = List(Hello, Hola, Guten tag)

scala> for (g <- greet) println(s"$g Scala! This is $name")
Hello Scala! This is Andrey Shevchenko
Hola Scala! This is Andrey Shevchenko
Guten tag Scala! This is Andrey Shevchenko

scala> for (g <- greet) println(s"$g Scala! This is ${name.reverse}")
Hello Scala! This is oknehcvehS yerdnA
Hola Scala! This is oknehcvehS yerdnA
Guten tag Scala! This is oknehcvehS yerdnA

scala> 
